    "PatCID leverages state-of-the-art document understanding models to ingest documents.",
    "As illustrated in Fig. 2, the ingestion pipeline uses three components: the document segmentation (DECIMER-Segmentation 23), the image classification (MolClassifier), and the chemical structure recognition (MolGrapher 24).",
    "The document segmentation module locates the position of chemical images in documents.",
    "Chemical images comprise molecular-structure images and Markushstructure 25 images.",
    "(Markush structures are sets of molecules defined using positional and frequency variation indications.)"
